Green Lantern (000 - 036 + Annuals) (2011 - Ongoing) (Digital) (Kingpin+Nahga-Empire)


This is the fifth volume of Green Lantern written by long time Green Lantern writer, Geoff Johns, following where War of the Green Lanterns left off, Sinestro, long time enemy of the Green Lantern Corps, has become a Green Lantern again, and no one knows why. Meanwhile, Hal Jordan is still with out his ring, and due to his over commitment to the Corps, his civilian life back on Earth is in shambles
